319694,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"結果只會係支那比錢印度,求印度佬自己走"},{"pid":"11555f8308eacd7b7d5eb4dd69bb020c1844a692","tid":319694,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撤僑係咩嚟</blockquote><br />\n咁撚蠢就google啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e11ddac7581f57761ec39467823fa72e4bc9460","tid":319694,"uid":2170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撒嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇錯+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978a98a2d41047d16d446b772afc2a9b363988dc","tid":319694,"uid":80841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:16:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撒嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b366ac633fc15916aa4d47d3d72f22e5f2acf345","tid":319694,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:17:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>撒嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇錯+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d9244a1f42bee49df927f63d0b1a7e381870b0","tid":319694,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>撒嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇錯+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n''中國準備撤嬌了''<br />\n以為印度使館真係會笑9 大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50628a32f9a842e6427f1676069ff66fbc67bc86","tid":319694,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>撒嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中文咁差點做五毛架 不過又係，唔係學歷差 社會垃圾都唔會去做五毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係有人比錢架? 介紹我呀喂<br />\n你真係以為大陸有派好多五毛黎香港?<br />\n駛撚咩<br />\n香港人係咩料呀<br />\n咪再自欺欺人<br />\n9成有學歷有地位既人係咩政治取態呀<br />\n社會垃圾會去做五毛?<br />\n成個垃圾會70個議員, 70個親共<br />\n個班人幾錢人工?<br />\n佢地行下街咋, 估下有幾多幾多香港人去笑住影張相<br />\n<br />\n成群成群ON9 後生<br />\n你以為共匪怕你地香港人?<br />\n怕你上街行? 怕你係網站打飛機?<br />\n得把口<br />\n得閒試下睇睇大陸網站<br />\n好多留言屌大陸勁過高登仔<br />\n思路清楚過香港人架<br />\n<br />\n我日日都想香港人仆街架<br />\n個個咁撚蠢又貪錢又怕死<br />\n貪錢仲死過大陸人<br />\n香港人不嬲唔死沒撚用<br />\n睇下黑警多唔多人想做<br />\n睇下淘寶多唔多人會用<br />\n睇下大陸劇多唔多人睇"}]}